description: Carefully harvested, this dandelion wreath has been made with love.
name: Dandelion wreath

description:
Cool white dress. A girl wearing this looks so innocent. 
She might not be.
name: White dress

description:
If I told you this costume is an exact copy of the elven emperor Alfas 
outfit, you wouldn't believe me.
name: Elven tyrant costume

description:
A gift from a dear friend who once travelled with the caravan but then
went away trying to find herself.
name: Melisa's ring

description:
Light brown dress with tan lace, the latest fashion. Peasant girls can 
only dream of owning such.
name: Plaid dress

description:
The dress still has lustre, but needs washing and sewing. Girls are 
still envious, but boys would like to see more.
name: Shabby dress

description:
The former lustre has gone. This rags won't give peasant boys even
a chance to daydream.
name: Ragged dress

description:
Wooden pendant in the shape of a cat's face. Someone worked very hard 
carving this cutest little thing.
name: Pendant with a cat

description:
Neat lazuli ring with a gemstone that resembles a night sky – deep dark 
blue with a cluster of bright stars.
name: Lazuli ring

description:
Cool and low-necked nightie. You feel calmer and warmer in it. At least
no one will accidentally see your naked body.
name: Nightie

description: A threadbare dress. You can see patches here and there.
name: Old dress

description:
Tradeswoman claims this dress once belonged to a noble woman. Interesting 
thing is, it strongly resembles the dresses of western prostitutes.
name: Dainteth frock

description: An old dress that tailor put to its original shape.
name: Restored old dress

description:
Wet white dress. It almost cries "Look, BOOBS!" 
(you need to wet it before using)
name: Wet white dress

description:
Only a person, who is hopelessly stupid or unfit for his position won’t 
apreciate this dress.
name: King’s dress

description:
This dress is an exact replica of nightie it was embroidered by the royal tailor 
himself. Allows you to look down on those who consider it an underwear.
name: Not a nightie

description:
Pine needles. Wolf fangs. Oak spikes... 
A nice name for these is yet to be thought of.
name: First mustache

description:
A serious pair of mustaches for a serious warlord. They look gorgeous and
require no care whatsoever.
name: Second mustache

description: Subtle pair worn by modern loudmouths, cowards and other slimeballs.
name: Third mustache

description:
A connoisseur's delicacy. They would make a nice addition to a fine broth.
If they hadn't been fake, that is.
name: Elven ears

description:
If I told you this costume is an exact copy of the elven emperor Alfas 
outfit, you wouldn't believe me.
name: Elven tyrant costume

description:
A pair once worn by one famous elven buffoon. It is rumored he could 
make his audience laugh without saying a single word.
name: Fourth mustache

description:
As legend has it, all the clothes of Nickolaus were soaked in the blood 
of the elven people. Wool framing is a human-made detail.
name: Nickolaus's hat

description:
A fine and elegant rose shaped pendant . Attracts attention towards it's wearer's
breasts. . . as if they don’t attract any attention themselves.
name: Rose pendant

description:
A pendant in the shape of Church's symbol that you can see on everything 
religious: robes, stained glasses, books, dishes, barrels, swords etc.
name: Wreath pendant

description: A delightful pendant in the shape of Lordy's holy face.
name: Lordy pendant

description:
A pendant in the shape of a wild cat, which hisses, arches it's back and bends 
it's tail.
name: Wild Cat pendant

description: Shell on a rope... regular shell... How cheap.
name: Shell pendant

description:
If you're gonna kill cute little animals, then try to use their little bodies 
to the max... Oh, yes, this amulet brings good luck.
name: Rabbit's foot amulet

description:
It’s not a necklace. Yes, they’re beads. Yes, they're on a string. But it’s not 
a necklace. I hope it doesn't occur to you to wear it around your neck.
name: Red necklace

description:
An expensive ring with a large ruby that sparkles so passionately in the sun. 
Many will agree to anything for such a jewel.
name: Ruby ring

description:
A perverted suit in which they indulge in animal debauchery and participate in
dirty games. Even cows will condemn it, let alone the Church.
name: Calf suit (wt)

description: Almost the perfect disguise for infiltrating the barn.
name: Cow horns and ears

description:
These horns are actually longer than cow horns and rather resemble the horns of
deamons... if deamons existed.
name: Cow horns

description:
A perverted suit in which they indulge in animal debauchery and participate in
dirty games. Even cows will condemn it, let alone the Church.
name: Calf suit

description: The amulet of acorn, twigs and strings made by little Rodinka for Rikhard.
name: Rikhard's Amulet

description: Gorgeous cow costume made of genuine leather. Nipples like a real ones.
name: Cow costume

description:
The lightweight short dress for the girl who wants to draw attention to herself.
It has great chest ventilation.
name: Noble Maiden's Dress

description:
The ordinary city girl's dress. Not expensive, but not cheap either. Not boring,
but not flashy.
name: Townswoman dress

description:
The amulet in the shape of an elven church symbol. Don't you dare wear that thing 
in public. And if you do, make sure you wash up afterward.
name: Elven cross

description:
The filigree tail, indistinguishable from the real thing. A work of art. If only
it didn't have to be inserted into the ass.
name: Cow tail

description:
Horns of either a cow or a demon, surprisingly do not attract attention to 
themselves.
name: Cow little horns

description:
A steel ring with an image of a split skull. Despite the unassuming quality,
the image is mildly disturbing.
name: Skull Ring
